{"tid":1632892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內奸出沒注意","createTime":"2019-10-07T00:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:55:22.000Z","uid":310758,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd75e0c5d5ae025fcc714597c617d5c1beb92ba","tid":1632892,"uid":310758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNMwgJW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNMwgJW.png&h=39875db8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjSLmaC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjSLmaC.png&h=b5685be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 一場成功既運動需要唔同角色配合，唔該一個二個睇清楚自己做緊既野係有效定冇效，咪為攪而攪，唔好諗住有文宣消毒就冇事，你識消毒黑媒都識繼續落毒，家中長輩已經好多淺黃變淺藍喇🤬🤬🤬🤬🤬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5e1209ff25f19c5803bb9d9a4c427a0d775442","tid":1632892,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:55:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的